            "content_html": "<main>\n    <p>\n\tSummary of BCD changes from <a href=\"\"><time title=\"Monday, 16 February 2026\">Monday, 16 February 2026</time></a> through <time title=\"Monday, 23 February 2026\">Monday, 23 February 2026</time></strong><a href=\"https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/weekly-completed/2026-02-23.html\" title=\"permalink\">🔗</a>\n    </p>\n    <hr>\n\n\n          <p class=\"callout\"><strong>25 new universal implementations</strong></p>\n          <section class=\"added implementations\">\n\t            <h4>API</h4>\n              <ol>\n                  <li>\n\n          \n\n                      <span>\n                        <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/API/Element/currentCSSZoom\">api ➞ Element ➞ currentCSSZoom</a>\n                      </span>\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n\n          \n\n                      <span>\n                        <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/API/ReadableByteStreamController\">api ➞ ReadableByteStreamController</a>\n                      </span>\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n\n          \n\n                      <span>\n                        <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/API/ReadableByteStreamController/byobRequest\">api ➞ ReadableByteStreamController ➞ byobRequest</a>\n                      </span>\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n\n          \n\n                      <span>\n                        <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/API/ReadableByteStreamController/close\">api ➞ ReadableByteStreamController ➞ close</a>\n                      </span>\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n\n          \n\n                      <span>\n                        <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/API/ReadableByteStreamController/desiredSize\">api ➞ ReadableByteStreamController ➞ desiredSize</a>\n                      </span>\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n\n          \n\n                      <span>\n                        <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/API/ReadableByteStreamController/enqueue\">api ➞ ReadableByteStreamController ➞ enqueue</a>\n                      </span>\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n\n          \n\n                      <span>\n                        <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/API/ReadableByteStreamController/error\">api ➞ ReadableByteStreamController ➞ error</a>\n                      </span>\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n\n          \n\n                      <span>\n                        <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Symbol/asyncIterator\">api ➞ ReadableStream ➞ @@asyncIterator</a>\n                      </span>\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n\n          \n\n                      <span>\n                        <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/API/ReadableStreamBYOBReader/ReadableStreamBYOBReader\">api ➞ ReadableStreamBYOBReader ➞ ReadableStreamBYOBReader</a>\n                      </span>\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n\n          \n\n                      <span>\n                        <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/API/ReadableStreamBYOBReader\">api ➞ ReadableStreamBYOBReader</a>\n                      </span>\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n\n          \n\n                      <span>\n                        <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/API/ReadableStreamBYOBReader/cancel\">api ➞ ReadableStreamBYOBReader ➞ cancel</a>\n                      </span>\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n\n          \n\n                      <span>\n                        <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/API/ReadableStreamBYOBReader/closed\">api ➞ ReadableStreamBYOBReader ➞ closed</a>\n                      </span>\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n\n          \n\n                      <span>\n                        <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/API/ReadableStreamBYOBReader/read\">api ➞ ReadableStreamBYOBReader ➞ read</a>\n                      </span>\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n\n          \n\n                      <span>\n                        <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/API/ReadableStreamBYOBReader/releaseLock\">api ➞ ReadableStreamBYOBReader ➞ releaseLock</a>\n                      </span>\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n\n          \n\n                      <span>\n                        <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/API/ReadableStreamBYOBRequest\">api ➞ ReadableStreamBYOBRequest</a>\n                      </span>\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n\n          \n\n                      <span>\n                        <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/API/ReadableStreamBYOBRequest/respond\">api ➞ ReadableStreamBYOBRequest ➞ respond</a>\n                      </span>\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n\n          \n\n                      <span>\n                        <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/API/ReadableStreamBYOBRequest/respondWithNewView\">api ➞ ReadableStreamBYOBRequest ➞ respondWithNewView</a>\n                      </span>\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n\n          \n\n                      <span>\n                        <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/API/ReadableStreamBYOBRequest/view\">api ➞ ReadableStreamBYOBRequest ➞ view</a>\n                      </span>\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n                      <span>api ➞ Response ➞ body ➞ readable_byte_stream\n                      </span>\n\n          \n\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n                      <span>api ➞ WebTransport ➞ byob_readers\n                      </span>\n\n          \n\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n                      <span>api ➞ WebTransport ➞ createUnidirectionalStream ➞ byob_readers\n                      </span>\n\n          \n\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n              </ol>\n\t            <h4>CSS</h4>\n              <ol>\n                  <li>\n                      <span>css ➞ properties ➞ font-size ➞ math\n                      </span>\n\n          \n\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n\n          \n\n                      <span>\n                        <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/CSS/Reference/Properties/math-depth\">css ➞ properties ➞ math-depth</a>\n                      </span>\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n                      <span>css ➞ properties ➞ math-depth ➞ auto-add\n                      \t<a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/mathml-core/#the-math-script-level-property:~:text&#x3D;Value%3A-,auto%2Dadd,-%7C%20add(%3Cinteger\"><img src=\"https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/imgs/spec2.svg\" alt=\"Spec link\"></a>\n                      </span>\n\n          \n\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n              </ol>\n\t            <h4>JAVASCRIPT</h4>\n              <ol>\n                  <li>\n\n          \n\n                      <span>\n                        <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Iterator/concat\">javascript ➞ builtins ➞ Iterator ➞ concat</a>\n                      </span>\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n              </ol>\n          </section>\n\n  <hr>\n  <ul id=\"prev-next\">\n  \t<li>Previous report: <a href=\"\"><time title=\"Monday, 16 February 2026\">Monday, 16 February 2026</time></a></li>\n  </ul>\n  <hr>\n  <footer>\n  \t<p>\n  \t<a href=\"https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/\">BCD Watch</a>: A service of <a href=\"https://igalia.com\"><img src=\"https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/imgs/igalia-logo.png\" alt=\"Igalia\"></a>\n  \t</p>\n  \t<p>\n  \tSubscribe: <a href=\"feed.rss\">RSS</a> • <a href=\"feed.atom\">Atom</a> • <a href=\"feed.json\">JSON</a>\n  \t</p>\n\t\t<div class=\"subfooter\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"details\">\n\t\t\tThis report was generated by diffing <a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data/releases/tag/v7.3.2\">v7.3.2</a> <small>(Friday, 13 February 2026)</small> and <a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data/releases/tag/v7.3.3\">v7.3.3</a> <small>(Friday, 20 February 2026)</small>\n\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t</div>\n  </footer>\n  </main>",
